<html>
<head>
  <meta name="viewport" content="user-scalable=yes,width=640px" />
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">
  <title>616邀请用户排行榜</title>
  <style>
    * {margin: 0px; padding: 0px;}
    body {text-align: center;}
    table#rank_table {margin: 10 auto; width: 560px; border-collapse: collapse;}
    table#rank_table th {padding: 18px; background-color: #ccc; font-size: 26px;}
    div.rank {font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; text-align: center; padding-top: 25px; width: 56px; height: 30px;}
    .rank1 {background-image: url('/images/advs/invite_user/1.png'); background-repeat:no-repeat; color: #FF3300;}
    .rank2 {background-image: url('/images/advs/invite_user/2.png');background-repeat:no-repeat; color: #FFCC00;}
    .rank3 {background-image: url('/images/advs/invite_user/3.png');background-repeat:no-repeat;color: #cccccc;}
    .rank4 {background-image: url('/images/advs/invite_user/4.png');background-repeat:no-repeat;color: #cccccc;}
    div.logo {margin: 4px; border: 1px solid #ccc; padding: 1px; width: 80px;}
    div.logo img {width: 80px; height: 80px;}
    div.name {font-size: 18px; margin: 4px;}
    div.num {font-size: 26px;}

    div.tip {text-align: left; font-size: 20px; color: #333; padding: 8px 16px; line-height: 130%;}
    div.tip p {margin: 8px 0px;}
    div.tip img {height: 26px;}
    div.tip h2 {font-size: 22px;}

    span.red {color: #EA609E;}
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="tip">
  <p>备注：<br/>
    1.感谢亲的参与和支持，邀好友,送豪礼活动结果将于揭晓了，请以下获奖者将自己的昵称、姓名、快递地址、手机号等统一提交给客服（QQ：1170979903），奖金获得者请向客服提交姓名、支付宝账号、手机号。<br/>
    2.如有反复注册或虚假邀请等行为，将取缔获奖资格。
    <br/>
  </p>
  <br/>
</div>

<table id='rank_table' border=1 bordercolor="#ccc">
  <tr>
    <th>排行</th>
    <th>上榜人</th>
    <th>邀请人数</th>
  </tr>
  <% @users.each_with_index do |user, index| %>
    <%
      clazz_name= case index
                    when 0
                      '1'
                    when 1..2
                      '2'
                    when 3..39
                      '3'
                    when 40..299
                      '4'
                  end
    %>
  <tr>
    <td align="center"><img src="/images/advs/invite_user/<%= clazz_name %>.png" alt="" style="height: 60px"/></td>
    <td align="center">
      <div class='logo'><img src="http://www.mamashai.com<%= user.logo.thumb140 %>"/></div>
      <div class="name"><%= user.name %></div>
    </td>
    <td align="center">
      <div class="name"><%= user.c||0 %> 人</div>
    </td>
  </tr>
  <% end %>
</table>
<br/>
<br/>
</body>
</html>
